    <tr>
     <td>This tutorial is a step in the <a href="../../forms/using/create-your-first-interactive-communication.md">Create your first Interactive Communication</a> series. It is recommended to follow the series in chronological sequence to understand, perform, and demonstrate the complete tutorial use case.</td> 
    </tr>
